= map

(from gem bundler-1.1.5)
=== Implementation from Thor
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  map(mappings=nil)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Maps an input to a task. If you define:

  map "-T" => "list"

Running:

  thor -T

Will invoke the list task.

==== Parameters
Hash[String|Array => Symbol]:
  Maps the string or the strings in the array to the given task.



